++ **Current Summary of Known Events**
[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-block name=http://lafundacionscp.wdfiles.com/local--files/koigarezaki-news-911-1998-ver/%E4%B8%8A%E7%A9%BA.jpg|caption=Thaumaturgical explosion immediately after entry, observed by NASA from space, circled by the author of this article.|width=240px|align=left]]
　The attacks began with the near-simultaneous hijacking of five aircraft - American Airlines Flight 11, United Airlines Flight 175, Delta Airlines Flight 1989, American Airlines Flight 77 and United Airlines Flight 93 - at around 8 a.m. (local time) on September 11. The CI executors used some sort of paratechnology in the cockpit and utilized mental manipulation on the pilots to send three of the planes (American Airlines Flight 11, United Airlines Flight 175 and Delta Airlines Flight 1989) to Manhattan, New York, and the other two (American Airlines Flight 77 and United Airlines Flight 93) to Washington, D.C.

　American Airlines Flight 77 and United Airlines Flight 93 then crashed into Pentagram Headquarters (The Pentagon) and Shanksville, Pennsylvania, respectively, in non-anomalous accidents that resulted in the destruction of their aircraft. However, the three Manhattan-bound planes crashed into the World Trade Center (WTC), and immediately after the collision, the entire area of Manhattan around the WTC collapsed into another dimension of nested crystalline structures.

　According to the International Center for the Study of Unified Thaumatology, these phenomena are similar in nature to the "Bodhisattva backlash" that usually occurs during incomplete manifestations of divine entities, but nothing of this magnitude has ever been observed before. According to Shugen Wang, 75, a member of the Bamboo Basket Peculiar Archaeology Association, a branch of the Chinese Society of Anomalous Things and Phenomena, it is likely that the CI used the ancient para-technological system of connecting collective consciousnesses of Prometheus Neurons, also employed in the 12/07 incident, in the descent ritual of another divine entity.

　"It is not known why the ritual failed, but if it had succeeded we would have witnessed the Polish nightmare of three years ago again.... an even greater one."
