++ **Movements of American Organizations**
[[include :scp-wiki:component:image-block name=http://lafundacionscp.wdfiles.com/local--files/koigarezaki-news-911-1998-ver/%E9%AD%9A.jpg|caption=Several mysterious creatures are being discovered around Manhattan. [*http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/yamizushi-hub The owner of a local sushi restaurant] says they moved when he cut them into three pieces.|width=240px|align=right]]
　Currently, it is not possible to observe the situation in the Manhattan area, and the safety of those who were within it at the time of the phenomenon is unknown. Another dimension is encroaching into ours, and the Foundation and GOC Special Operations Headquarters based in New York are busy day and night responding to the situation.

　In addition to countermeasures against the erosion of other dimensions, a method of accessing Manhattan through other parallel dimensions is currently being developed, and space engineers and casters around the world, including [[[gumiho|Mrs. Hoya]]] from Dinodon's Hand and a group of researchers from the RIGAIKEN Research Institute, are meeting here in New York one after another for this project. The task force appears to be planning a search and rescue operation to locate survivors as soon as possible, establishment of this route is a top priority.

　Additionally, regarding the creatures found around Manhattan, the Foundation states that it is likely that they are Tartarean entities that have invaded through spatial overlap with another dimension, and a joint unit of demon hunters is planned to be formed, led by Dr. Alto Clef of the Foundation. Currently, they are working with [[[scp-4967|holy water generation systems]]] and relocating anti-Tartarean equipment from [[[scp-4661|Las Vegas]]] to New York.

　On the other hand, the GOC appears to be willing to blow up Manhattan Island if erosion continues in another dimension: in 1988, the GOC partially destroyed [[[nx-03|the area around Hy-Brasil]]] [[[lte-0851-cetus|with a directed nuclear energy weapon]]]] targeted against the Crocosquid (also known as the Crocodile Kraken), and is in fact deploying similar weapons around New York City. The Pentagram, the Pentagon's occult division, is in crisis, and the US Government is urging the GOC to act with caution, but the GOC, after regretting the delay and damage caused by the 12/07 incident, seems to be maintaining an uncompromising stance in order to bring the situation under control as soon as possible. It can be said that intervention is only a matter of time, and the delay in the Foundation's response is to blame.　【Takayuki Hirosue and George R.】
